snippet.title: Visions of Mana | Launch Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Visions of Mana is a brand new title in this series revolving around the sacred sword and mana.
Val, the protagonist, and his childhood friend Hinna, the newly appointed Alm of Fire, set off on a journey to the Mana Tree. Visions of Mana is now available for pre-order on PS5™, PS4™, Xbox Series X|S consoles and PC via Windows and Steam®.

 Launching August 29th 2024.
